ed="T" n="0775c20"/><persName key="A010505">釋智藏</persName>，姓<name>黃</name>氏，<placeName key="PL000000019671">豫章上高</placeName>人也。父為<placeName key="PL000000018628">洪州</placeName><lb
ed="T" n="0775c21"/><anchor xml:id="beg0775sgsz16"/><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>椽</sic><corr>掾</corr></choice><anchor xml:id="end0775sgsz16"/>。<persName key="A010505">藏</persName>隨父入<placeName key="PL000000023874">報國寺</placeName><ptr target="#n1482"/>，見供奉<persName key="A010506">皓月</persName>講《涅槃<lb
ed="T" n="0775c22"/>經》，<anchor xml:id="beg0775sgsz17"/>微<anchor xml:id="end0775sgsz17"/>體經意，樂入佛門。年甫十三，割恩愛，<lb
ed="T" n="0775c23"/>辭父母，於<placeName key="PL000000018582">開元寺</placeName><persName key="A010508">宗<roleName>法師</roleName></persName>所受學。後修禪<lb
ed="T" n="0775c24"/>法，證<persName key="A003623">大寂一<roleName>公</roleName></persName>宗要矣。<date from-iso="+0780-02-15" key="j20059942006346" to-iso="+0781-02-01"><name>建中</name>元年</date>，入<placeName key="PL000000042189">長安</placeName>。<lb
ed="T" n="0775c25"/><persName key="A010507"><choice resp="sgsz"><sic>廬</sic><corr>盧</corr></choice>元顥</persName>素奉其道，舉奏入內供養，勅令住<lb
ed="T" n="0775c26"/><placeName key="PL000000042515">華嚴寺</placeName>。輦轂之間，玄學者孔熾，就<persName key="A010505">藏</persName>之門，<lb
ed="T" n="0775c27"/>若海水之歸投琴之壑矣。<date from-iso="+0835-02-06" key="j20260742026427" to-iso="+0836-01-25"><name><anchor xml:id="beg0775sgsz18"/>太<anchor xml:id="end0775sgsz18"/>和</name>九年</date>終于<lb
ed="T" n="0775c28"/><ref type="place" target="#PL000000042515">住寺</ref>，<date key="j20261442026144" when-iso="+0835-04-17">三月十二日</date>入塔焉。</p>
